casebody.data:
Artemio M. ILAGAN, et ux., petitioners
v.
Engracia UNGACTA, et al. No. 12-723. Supreme Court of the United States April 15, 2013.

Motion of National Federation of Independent Business Small Business Legal Center, et al. for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Guam denied.
